race.comment: EMERALD COURT (4) is a leader bringing two narrow defeats from Colac. Draws inside and a senior rider replaces the 3kg apprentice. Ready to win and finds the right race. BANGHOLME (1) peaks and he spiked his figures at Stawell last time. That form would see him right in the finish. REDEMPTION TIME (3) has been plain her last two but the form prior reads well enough. May be worth another chance. HERE'S TO JANE (7) tumbles in weight off a placing at the picnics. Missed by 1L at Colac prior and that would have her around the mark. DEEP CORE (9) mixes the form but has his share of ability. He won't be far away putting his best foot forward.
